This sample shows how to work with Infragistics Tooltip manager control.

Learn how to change various properties of tooltips - background, foreground, and border colours. The sample shows how to set a tooltip 
title, how to format the text or add a custom image to tooltips or change the tooltip's display style. It also gives an example of invoking the toolpis manually, how to control 
the delay before the tooltip is displayed and for how long.


